      "textUthmaniTajweed": "إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لَّذِينَ فَتَنُو<tajweed class=slnt>اْ</tajweed> <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْمُؤْمِنِينَ وَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْمُؤْمِنَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>تِ ثُ<tajweed class=ghunnah>مّ</tajweed>َ لَمْ يَتُوبُو<tajweed class=slnt>اْ</tajweed> فَلَهُمْ عَذَابُ جَهَ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َمَ وَلَهُمْ عَذَابُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْحَر<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ِي</tajweed><tajweed class=qalaqah>ق</tajweed>ِ <span class=end>١٠</span>",
